    {
      "text": "\n    \n      \n              \n  \n    \n\n\n\n\n\n  \n\n          \n  \n    Jesse Watters wants to pretend the end of Roe is no big deal. Reality keeps proving him wrong\n    \n  ",
      "url": "/jesse-watters/jesse-watters-repeatedly-fails-efforts-suppress-critical-reporting-ohio-ten-year-old"
    },
    {
      "text": "\n    \n      \n              \n  \n    \n\n\n\n\n\n  \n\n          \n  \n\n    \n      Local print and digital coverage often caved to anti-abortion spin after Roe was overturned\n\n\n      \n\n\n      \n        \n          Article\n    \n    \n  \n\n    \n  \n  07/18/22 9:37 AM EDT\n\n    \n  ",
      "url": "/local-news/local-print-and-digital-coverage-often-caved-anti-abortion-spin-after-roe-was-overturned"
    },
    {
      "text": "\n    \n      \n              \n  \n    \n\n\n\n\n\n  \n\n          \n  \n\n    \n      Tucker Carlson is in Iowa selling cheap hats and streaming subscriptions\n\n\n      \n\n\n      \n        \n          Article\n    \n    \n  \n\n    \n  \n  07/16/22 1:42 PM EDT\n\n    \n  ",
      "url": "/tucker-carlson/tucker-carlson-iowa-selling-cheap-hats-and-streaming-subscriptions"
    },
    {
      "text": "\n    \n      \n              \n  \n    \n\n\n\n\n\n  \n\n          \n  \n\n    \n      One America News is promoting election deniers running for key state offices in midterms\n\n\n      \n\n\n      \n        \n          Article\n    \n    \n  \n\n    \n  \n  07/18/22 10:13 AM EDT\n\n    \n  ",
      "url": "/one-america-news-network/one-america-news-promoting-election-deniers-running-key-state-executive"
    },
    {
      "text": "\n    \n      \n              \n  \n    \n\n\n\n\n\n  \n\n          \n  \n\n    \n      Allie Beth Stuckey teeters between culture war crusader and fundamentalist Christian propagandist  \n\n\n      \n\n\n      \n        \n          Article\n    \n    \n  \n\n    \n  \n  07/14/22 9:23 AM EDT\n\n    \n  ",
      "url": "/blazetv/allie-beth-stuckey-teeters-between-culture-war-crusader-and-fundamentalist-christian"
    },
    {
      "text": "\n    \n      \n              \n  \n    \n\n\n\n\n\n  \n\n          \n  \n\n    \n      These media figures discredited a report on a 10-year-old girl needing an abortion. There was just an arrest in the case.\n\n\n      \n\n\n      \n        \n          Research/Study\n    \n    \n  \n\n    \n  \n  07/13/22 5:06 PM EDT\n\n    \n  ",
      "url": "/fox-news/these-media-figures-discredited-report-10-year-old-girl-needing-medical-abortion-there-was"
    },
    {
      "text": "\n    \n      \n              \n  \n    \n\n\n\n\n\n  \n\n          \n  \n\n    \n      The Wall Street Journal issues a non-apology for denying a 10-year-old\u2019s rape\n\n\n      \n\n\n      \n        \n          Article\n    \n    \n  \n\n    \n  \n  07/14/22 11:30 AM EDT\n\n    \n  ",
      "url": "/wall-street-journal/wall-street-journal-issues-non-apology-denying-10-year-olds-rape"
    },
    {
      "text": "\n    \n      \n              \n  \n    \n\n\n\n\n\n  \n\n          \n  \n\n    \n      Laura Ingraham\u2019s reaction to her friend Pat Cipollone\u2019s testimony shows how Fox was complicit in Trump's coup\n\n\n      \n\n\n      \n        \n          Article\n    \n    \n  \n\n    \n  \n  07/13/22 1:14 PM EDT\n\n    \n  ",
      "url": "/january-6-insurrection/laura-ingrahams-reaction-her-friend-pat-cipollones-testimony-shows-how-fox"
    },
    {
      "text": "\n    \n      \n              \n  \n    \n\n\n\n\n\n  \n\n          \n  \n\n    \n      In the first half of 2022, Fox News feverishly pushed debunked, racist, and inflammatory narratives about immigration and migrants \n\n\n      \n\n\n      \n        \n          Article\n    \n    \n  \n\n    \n  \n  07/12/22 1:52 PM EDT\n\n    \n  ",
      "url": "/immigration/first-half-2022-fox-news-feverishly-pushed-debunked-racist-and-inflammatory-narratives"
